short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Filter and sort your GitHub PR overview

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Please note that this exension is absolutely bare bones right now. More features and customizability will be added in the future.

This extension adds a new button to the GitHub PR overview: "Priority"
This directs you to the list of requested reviews, but hides all PRs from the user "dependabot".
